      "text": "<p><code>dropElements([0, 1, 0, 1], function(n) {return n === 1;})</code> treba da vrati <code>[1, 0, 1]</code>.</p>",
      "testString": "assert.deepEqual(\r\n  dropElements([0, 1, 0, 1], function (n) {\r\n    return n === 1;\r\n  }),\r\n  [1, 0, 1]\r\n);"
    },
